# Vendored third-party C4D runtime deps (numpy/scipy). Reproducible from
# tools/vendor_c4d_deps.ps1 (Windows) and tools/vendor_mac_deps.ps1 (macOS),
# pinned to exact versions, so they are not tracked in git (standard practice
# for re-fetchable dependencies, like node_modules / venv). Run those scripts
# after cloning, before packaging a release.
vendor/
